emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five women and man, with P. L. Prattis seated on left and Jessie Vann standing on right, on stage of A. Leo Weil School during the "Favorite Churchwoman's" contest award program
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 29, 1952, pg. 1 reads: "Churchwomen's Award Program Was A Colorful Affair - Nearly all of the entrants in Courier's "Favorite Churchwoman's" contest were present on Thursday, Nov. 20, at A. Leo Weil School to receive their rewards and gifts..."
